data.description: Welcome to this must-see amazing 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom that includes a very large loft & an extra large den. property! This stunning residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and spacious living. This home is located in the desired neighborhood of Wyndham Hill part of Erie Schools. Walk into your foyer & to the left is your formal dining that leads through a butlers pantry, continue into your open concept kitchen & family room.  The kitchen has a large center island, gas stove, double ovens & pantry.  Family room features built-ins.  The main level features a 1/2 bath & a large den w/french doors, rounding off w/laundry on the main level.  Head upstairs to the primary bedroom featuring a 5-piece bath, walk-in closet, & coffered ceilings.  3 more bedrooms & a massive loft.  1 of the secondary bedrooms has a private bath attached & walk-in closet. Home includes a full size unfinished basement & well kept back yard w/large concrete patio expanding the width of the home. To top it off this 3 car garage is oversized! Also included are dual heating & air conditioning systems, 1 for the basement/main level  & the 2nd for the upstairs. This home has it all and will not last in this sought after neighborhood, schedule your showing today!   Listing Company has negotiated with seller to pay a buyers agent the advertised commission.  Nestled in a community that offers a pool and multiple parks, this residence is ideal for families seeking a vibrant neighborhood environment. Additionally, its central location provides easy access to major cities - just 30 minutes to Denver, Boulder, Fort Collins, and the Airport. For nature enthusiasts, the picturesque town of Estes Park is a short 45-minute drive away. With its blend of modern amenities, energy efficiency, and prime location, this property is more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your own! Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Showings Start 11-15-2023
